ORGANIZER;CN=Noah Bohren:mailto:bohren.noah@gmail.com
DESCRIPTION:Public PhD defense at HEC Lausanne followed by an apéritif.\n\nPresentation: "What Is an Economist?"\n\nThe presentation will offer an accessible introduction to how economists think about causality, experiments, and human decision-making, using examples from research on artificial intelligence, online ratings, and behavior.\n\nGuests are warmly invited to join the apéritif following the defense.\n\nInvitation page and RSVP:\nhttps://www.notion.so/noahbohren/Noah-Bohren-PhD-Defense-395afac8369b801bbd50d1350a146eb9?source=copy_link\n\nMicrosoft Teams:\nhttps://teams.microsoft.com/meet/332591362192789?p=pgndRiW5fzDMtmyrF7\n\nMeeting ID: 332 591 362 192 789\nPasscode: Fz3Wf7z8
